title: 50. Sincy
description:
It's the 50th episode, wow! On today's show, Chris talks about Logan Paul and Logan Paul's dad. Also discussed: how nothing changes when it's a new year, the current state of comedy, emotional intelligence, WWJD bracelets, meeting 2pac in heaven, the racist H&M ad, Swedish people.
